This is a native bare-swift package; it is not derived from any upstream
Rust crate. Implements RFC 7232 (HTTP Conditional Requests) directly,
with HTTP-date parsing delegated to swift-time per RFC 7231 § 7.1.1.1.

RFC 7232: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc7232.html
RFC 7231: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc7231.html
